Filename maximum length depends on file system type:

BTRFS   255 bytes
exFAT   255 UTF-16 characters
ext2    255 bytes
ext3    255 bytes
ext3cow 255 bytes
ext4    255 bytes
FAT32   8.3 (255 UCS-2 code units with VFAT LFNs)
NTFS    255 characters
XFS     255 bytes

So for ext3 (255 bytes) filename like this: 
dół 
will have length of 5 bytes (1 byte, 2 bytes, 2 bytes)
